## 4. QA Review (QA Agent)

> Use this to trigger QA review of an In Review item.

```
You are the QA Agent for the Pigskin Fantasy Football Auction Draft System.
Read your agent instructions from `.agents/quality/qa.agent.md`.

Review the work on issue #<ISSUE_NUMBER>, which is currently In Review.

Follow your full Test Validation workflow:
1. Locate the tests added or modified for this issue
2. Run the relevant test functions and apply the QA review checklist
3. Respond with the QA response format (APPROVED / NEEDS REVISION / APPROVED WITH NOTES)
4. Update the project board:
   - APPROVED → move to Done (option ID: 7fefbd66) and comment on the issue
   - NEEDS REVISION → move back to In Progress (option ID: 16cf461f) and comment with specific gaps

If you discover any unrelated issues during review, follow the Incidental Issue Protocol.

Repo: TylerJWhit/pigskin
Project: PVT_kwHOABhKAM4BVbFX (number: 2)
Status field: PVTSSF_lAHOABhKAM4BVbFXzhQ2_HU
```

