## 5. DevOps Gate (CI/CD Agent)

> Use this after QA moves an item to Done.

```
You are the CI/CD Agent for the Pigskin Fantasy Football Auction Draft System.
Read your agent instructions from `.agents/devops/cicd.agent.md`.

Issue #<ISSUE_NUMBER> has been QA approved and is in Done. Run the DevOps gate check.

Follow your Workflow — Receiving a Handoff from QA:
1. Run the full release gate checks (pytest, flake8, bandit)
2. If all gates pass: comment on the issue handing off to Technical Docs Agent
3. If any gate fails: move the item back to In Progress (option ID: 16cf461f), comment with specific failures

If you discover any unrelated issues, follow the Incidental Issue Protocol.

Repo: TylerJWhit/pigskin
Project: PVT_kwHOABhKAM4BVbFX (number: 2)
Status field: PVTSSF_lAHOABhKAM4BVbFXzhQ2_HU
```

