## Project Board Quick Reference

| Status | Option ID | Set by |
|--------|-----------|--------|
| Backlog | `0ed47968` | Automation |
| Ready | `faa0aeb8` | Project Manager |
| In Progress | `16cf461f` | Dev Agent |
| In Review | `68c4a78a` | Dev Agent |
| Done | `7fefbd66` | QA Agent |
| Closed | `a0358230` | Docs Agent |

```bash
# Look up project item ID for any issue
gh project item-list 2 --owner TylerJWhit --format json \
  | jq -r '.items[] | select(.content.number == <ISSUE_NUMBER>) | .id'

# Move item to any status
gh project item-edit --project-id "PVT_kwHOABhKAM4BVbFX" --id "<ITEM_ID>" \
  --field-id "PVTSSF_lAHOABhKAM4BVbFXzhQ2_HU" --single-select-option-id "<OPTION_ID>"
```
